List generator

Source: R/list.R
list_.Rd

This will generate lists with contents corresponding to the values generated by the input generators.

Usage

list_(...)

Arguments

...

Quickcheck generators

Value

A quickcheck_generator generator

Examples

list_(integer_(), logical_()) |> show_example()
#> [[1]]
#> [1]  7660  7949 -1284     0  6959 -1116
#> 
#> [[2]]
#> [1] FALSE  TRUE FALSE FALSE  TRUE  TRUE  TRUE FALSE
#> 
list_(a = any_vector(), b = any_vector()) |> show_example()
